{"title_page": "Sho Kagami", "text_new": "{{Infobox football biography\n|name=Sho Kagami\n|image=\n|image_size=\n|alt=\n|caption=\n|fullname=Sho Kagami\n|birth_date={{Birth date and age|1994|4|22}}\n|birth_place=[[Shizuoka Prefecture|Shizuoka]], [[Japan]]\n|height={{Height|m=1.74}}\n|position=[[Forward (association football)|Forward]]\n|currentclub= \n|clubnumber=\n|years1=2013\u20132016|clubs1=[[Shimizu S-Pulse]]|caps1=1|goals1=0\n|years2=2014\u20132015|clubs2=\u2192[[J.League U-22 Selection]]|caps2=14|goals2=2\n|years3=2016|clubs3=\u2192[[Fujieda MYFC]] (loan)|caps3=|goals3=\n|nationalyears1=|nationalteam1=|nationalcaps1=|nationalgoals1=\n|medaltemplates=\n|club-update=December 31, 2015\n|nationalteam-update=\n}}\n\n{{Nihongo|'''Sho Kagami'''|\u52a0\u8cc0\u7f8e \u7fd4|Kagami Sho|born April 22, 1994 in [[Shizuoka Prefecture|Shizuoka]]}} is a [[Japan]]ese [[Association football|football]] player.<ref>[https://data.j-league.or.jp/SFIX04/?player_id=11387 J.League Data Site]{{in lang|ja}}</ref> He plays for [[Fujieda MYFC]].\n\n==Playing career==\nSho Kagami joined to [[Shimizu S-Pulse]] in 2013. In June 2016, he moved to [[Fujieda MYFC]].\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n*{{J.League player|11387}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Kagami, Sho}}\n[[Category:1994 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Association football people from Shizuoka Prefecture]]\n[[Category:Japanese footballers]]\n[[Category:J1 League players]]\n[[Category:J2 League players]]\n[[Category:J3 League players]]\n[[Category:Shimizu S-Pulse players]]\n[[Category:Fujieda MYFC players]]\n[[Category:J.League U-22 Selection players]]\n[[Category:Association football forwards]]\n\n\n{{Japan-footy-forward-1990s-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox football biography\n|name=Sho Kagami\n|image=\n|image_size=\n|alt=\n|caption=\n|fullname=Sho Kagami\n|birth_date={{Birth date and age|1994|4|22}}\n|birth_place=[[Shizuoka Prefecture|Shizuoka]], [[Japan]]\n|height={{Height|m=1.74}}\n|position=[[Forward (association football)|Forward]]\n|currentclub= \n|clubnumber=\n|years1=2013\u20132016|clubs1=[[Shimizu S-Pulse]]|caps1=1|goals1=0\n|years2=2014\u20132015|clubs2=\u2192[[J.League U-22 Selection]]|caps2=14|goals2=2\n|years3=2016|clubs3=\u2192[[Fujieda MYFC]] (loan)|caps3=|goals3=\n|nationalyears1=|nationalteam1=|nationalcaps1=|nationalgoals1=\n|medaltemplates=\n|club-update=December 31, 2015\n|nationalteam-update=\n}}\n\n{{Nihongo|'''Sho Kagami'''|\u52a0\u8cc0\u7f8e \u7fd4|Kagami Sho|born April 22, 1994 in [[Shizuoka Prefecture|Shizuoka]]}} is a [[Japan]]ese [[Association football|football]] player.<ref>[https://data.j-league.or.jp/SFIX04/?player_id=11387 J.League Data Site]{{in lang|ja}}</ref> He plays for [[Fujieda MYFC]].\n\n==Playing career==\nSho Kagami joined to [[Shimizu S-Pulse]] in 2013. In June 2016, he moved to [[Fujieda MYFC]].\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n*{{J.League player|11387}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Kagami, Sho}}\n[[Category:1994 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Association football people from Shizuoka Prefecture]]\n[[Category:Japanese footballers]]\n[[Category:J1 League players]]\n[[Category:J2 League players]]\n[[Category:J3 League players]]\n[[Category:Shimizu S-Pulse players]]\n[[Category:Fujieda MYFC players]]\n[[Category:J.League U-22 Selection players]]\n[[Category:Association football forwards]]\n\n\n{{Japan-footy-forward-stub}}\n", "name_user": "Joeykai", "label": "safe", "comment": "\u2192\u200eExternal links:clean up", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sho_Kagami"}
{"title_page": "Shion Niwa", "text_new": "{{Infobox football biography\n| name                = Shion Niwa <br> \u4e39\u7fbd\u8a69\u6e29\n| fullname            = Shion Niwa\n| birth_date          = {{birth date and age|df=yes|1994|6|18}}\n| birth_place         = United States\n| height={{height|m=1.78}}\n| position            = [[Forward (association football)|Forward]]\n| currentclub         = [[Ehime FC]]\n| clubnumber          = 15\n| youthyears1         = 2013\u20132016 | youthclubs1 = [[Meiji University]]\n| years1              = 2017\u2013 | clubs1 = [[Ehime FC]] | caps1 = 68 | goals1 = 8\n| club-update         = 1 January 2019\n| nationalteam-update = 30 May 2017\n}}\n\n{{Nihongo|'''Shion Niwa'''|\u4e39\u7fbd \u8a69\u6e29|Niwa Shion|born 18 June 1994}}, is a Japanese professional [[association football|footballer]] who plays as [[Forward (association football)|forward]] for [[Ehime FC]].\n\n==Club statistics==\n''Updated to 23 February 2018''.<ref>Nippon Sports Kikaku Publishing inc./\u65e5\u672c\u30b9\u30dd\u30fc\u30c4\u4f01\u753b\u51fa\u7248\u793e, [https://www.amazon.co.jp/J1-J3%E9%81%B8%E6%89%8B%E5%90%8D%E9%91%91%E3%83%8F%E3%83%B3%E3%83%87%E3%82%A3%E7%89%88-2018-NSK-MOOK/dp/4905411521 \"J1&J2&J3\u9078\u624b\u540d\u9451\u30cf\u30f3\u30c7\u30a3\u7248 2018 (NSK MOOK)\"], 7 February 2018, Japan, {{ISBN|978-4905411529}} (p. 212 out of 289)</ref><ref>Nippon Sports Kikaku Publishing inc./\u65e5\u672c\u30b9\u30dd\u30fc\u30c4\u4f01\u753b\u51fa\u7248\u793e, [https://www.amazon.co.jp/2017-J1-J3%E9%81%B8%E6%89%8B%E5%90%8D%E9%91%91-NSK-MOOK/dp/4905411424/ref=pd_sim_14_1/356-9491148-0114816?_encoding=UTF8&psc=1&refRID=BA8BN4Y0F97GNWKQM78H \"2017 J1&J2&J3\u9078\u624b\u540d\u9451 (NSK MOOK)\"], 8 February 2017, Japan, {{ISBN|978-4905411420}} (p. 193 out of 289)</ref>\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align:center;\"\n|-\n! colspan=3 | Club performance\n! colspan=2 | League\n! colspan=2 | Cup\n! colspan=2 | Total\n|-\n! Season\n! Club\n! League\n! Apps !! Goals\n! Apps